---
import davidPotraitImgPath from "/assets/img/about/david_portrait.jpeg";
---

<section
  id="about"
  class="flex h-fit flex-col gap-4 bg-[#F9F9F9] p-4 md:grid md:place-items-center py-8"
>
  <div class="flex w-full flex-col space-y-8 md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-4xl">
    <h1
      class="font-montserrat-bold text-3xl font-extrabold text-accent-primary sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl"
    >
      About Me
    </h1>

    <div class="flex flex-col space-y-8 md:flex-row md:space-x-6 md:space-y-0">
      <div class="grid w-full place-items-center">
        <div
          class="h-64 w-64 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-slate-50 shadow-lg md:h-full md:rounded-md"
        >
          <img
            class="h-full w-full object-cover object-center"
            src={davidPotraitImgPath}
            alt="david-reyes-portrait"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="flex h-auto flex-col py-0 md:py-2 lg:py-8">
        <!-- Description -->
        <p
          class="font-libre-franklin text-lg text-foreground-primary md:text-xl"
        >
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do
          eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad
          minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut
          aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in
          reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla
          pariatur.
        </p>

        <div class="flex-1"></div>

        <h2
          class="mb-2 mt-4 font-iosevka text-lg font-bold text-accent-primary md:text-xl"
        >
          Things I like
        </h2>

        <div class="w-full pl-8">
          <ul class="w-fit list-disc marker:text-accent-primary">
            <li
              class="font-libre-franklin text-lg text-foreground-primary md:text-xl"
            >
              <span class="font-bold">Books:</span> 1984, Dracula, The Odyssey, and
              For Whom the Bell Tolls.
            </li>
            <li
              class="font-libre-franklin text-lg text-foreground-primary md:text-xl"
            >
              <span class="font-bold">Shows:</span> The Office, It's Always Sunny
              in Philadelphia, The Mandalorian, Attack On Titan, Jojo's Bizzare Adventure
              and Chainsaw Man.
            </li>
            <li
              class="font-libre-franklin text-lg text-foreground-primary md:text-xl"
            >
              <span class="font-bold">Music:</span> Interpol, Radiohead, CAS, and
              Angus & Julia Stone.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
